                <div class="col-lg-8 lead">
                    <h1 class="display-3 text-nowrap">Innovation Tracker</h1>
                    <p>Manufactoring and Automotive Tool</p>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-8 mb-0 mb-lg-3">
                    <div class="py-4 border-top border-bottom my-3">
                        <div class="row align-items-center">
                            <div class="col-auto ">
                                <p class="mb-0 font-size-5" >Role<br><span class="small">UX Designer</span></p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-lg d-flex justify-content-lg-start mt-3 mt-lg-0">
                                <p class="mb-0 font-size-5">Timeframe<br><span class="small">4 Weeks</span></p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <h2>Overview</h2>
                    <p>A multinational tire manufactoring company would like a way for their employees to submit company-specific innovation ideas. This tool would allow stakeholders to gather insights, and track the process. In my role as Senior UX, I led the discover, design, assisted development, and presented to stakeholders.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-10 mb-3 mb-lg-3">
                                <figure class="figure mb-0 border">
                                    <picture>
                                        <source srcset="assets/images/photos/Innovation_plan.png" type="image/webp">
                                        <source srcset="assets/images/photos/Innovation_plan.png" type="image/png"> 
                                        <img src="assets/images/photos/Innovation_plan.png" alt="photo-62" class="figure-img img-fluid w-100">
                                    </picture>

                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-8 mb-0 mb-lg-2">
                    <blockquote class="blockquote bqspecial p-4 text-secondary text-left font-weight-normal my-6 font-size-4"><h3>Goal</h3>The goal is to provide a functioning MVP in four weeks to allow employees, executives, and DXC leadership to submit innovations, gather insights, and track the process.</blockquote>

                    <h2>Process</h2>
                    <h4>Creative during COVID</h4>
                    <p>Coronavirus stay at home order made it essential to be creative with how to collaborate using video to define user stories.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-lg-10 mb-0 mb-lg-3 text-center">
                        <figure class="figure mb-0">
                            <picture>
                                 <source srcset="assets/images/photos/Innovation_discovery.png" type="image/webp">
                                 <source srcset="assets/images/photos/Innovation_discovery.png" type="image/png"> 
                                <img src="assets/images/photos/Innovation_discovery.png" alt="photo-62" class="figure-img img-fluid w-50">
                            </picture>
                        </div>
                    
                    <div class="col-lg-8 mb-0 mb-lg-2">         
                    <h4>I Heart Figma</h4>
                    <p>After kickoff meeting and review of requirements with the client, I quickly jumped into wireframes to allow for future meetings to center around visual solutions. This focuses the team on functionality â€¨and defining scope.</p>
                    
                    <p>We utilized Figma's ability to co-collaborate with the client and development team to iron out details of the low-fidelity wireframes during week one. </p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="col-lg-10 mb-3 mb-lg-3">
                        <figure class="figure mb-0">
                            <picture>
                                 <source srcset="assets/images/photos/Innovation_lowfid.png" type="image/webp">
                                 <source srcset="assets/images/photos/Innovation_lowfid.png" type="image/png"> 
                                <img src="assets/images/photos/Innovation_lowfid.png" alt="photo-62" class="figure-img img-fluid w-100">
                            </picture>
                        </div>
                    
                    <div class="col-lg-8 mb-0 mb-lg-2"> 
                    <h4>Design by committee</h4>
                    <p>Next week, we solidified the high-fidelity designs with the team so they could begin to develop. They had been developing already based on the low-fidelity designs.</p>
                    <p>Beginning of week 3 we had a very successful demo to the client that involved 3 screens and basic functionality working on the local development environment.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-lg-8 mb-0 mb-lg-2"> 
                        <h4>Sprint to the finish</h4>
                        <p>End of week 3, we had more screens to demo. Throughout the build, I provided guidance to the development team via screenshots. There were less and less revisions each time.</p>
                        <p>Development was complete by end of day Monday at the beginning of week 4. We had time to perfect and even code a few stretch goals to wow the client.</p>
                        </div>
                    
