                    <blockquote class="blockquote bqspecial p-4 text-secondary text-left font-weight-normal my-3 font-size-4"><h3>Result</h3>Demo to leadership and account team went smoothly. Use case created and all set to sell. Fingers crossed!
                        Update: The account team has re-skinned the application for two other clients. We will know soon if sold.</blockquote>
